text: Nobody 2 is an upcoming American action-thriller movie. It is expected to be released on August 15, 2025. It was directed by Timo Tjahjanto and stars Bob Odenkirk, Connie Nielsen, RZA, Sharon Stone, Colin Hanks, John Ortiz, and Christopher Lloyd. It is a sequel to the 2021 movie Nobody.
